<p><img src="data:image/jpeg;base64,"></p><p>1. After your video information is saved, you need to add the video to an album in Vimeo.</p><p>2. Hover over the Plastipak P in the top right and click on Video.</p><p>3. Locate your video (in order by upload date/time) and hover over Added column.</p><p>4. Click on the Settings icon.</p><p>5. Scroll down the column on the left to search for Albums.</p><p>6. Select the desired album(s) and click Save.</p><p>7. Log out of Vimeo.</p>
